flowchart TB
  subgraph DeviceBox[Windows 10 IoT device]
    Startup[COMP-DEVICE-001\nStartupTask]
    Detector[COMP-DEVICE-002\nLocalFaceDetector]
    Persister[COMP-DEVICE-003\nAzureImagePersister]
    DevConfig[COMP-DEVICE-004\nDeviceConfiguration]
    Startup --> Detector
    Detector --> Persister
    Persister --> DevConfig
  end

  subgraph BackendBox[Backend host]
    ApiHost[COMP-API-001\nBackend host]
    DeviceApi[COMP-API-002\nDeviceController]
    ApiHost --> DeviceApi
  end

  subgraph JobBox[WebJob process]
    JobHost[COMP-JOB-001\nWebJob host]
    Processor[COMP-JOB-002\nEvent processor]
    JobHost --> Processor
  end

  subgraph CommonBox[Common library]
    IotSvc[COMP-INTEG-001\nIotHubService]
    DdbSvc[COMP-PERSIST-001\nDocumentDbService]
    FaceSvc[COMP-INTEG-002\nFaceApiService]
    StorageSvc[COMP-INTEG-003\nStorageService]
    DTOs[DTOs\nDevice Event Visit]
  end

  subgraph AzureBox[Azure managed infrastructure]
    IoTHub[IoT Hub]
    Blob[Blob Storage]
    SB[Service Bus queue]
    DocDB[DocumentDB]
    Face[Face API]
    Emotion[Emotion API provisioned only]
  end

  DevConfig -->|INT-API-001| DeviceApi
  DeviceApi --> IotSvc
  IotSvc -->|INT-IOTHUB-REG-001| IoTHub
  Persister -->|INT-STORAGE-UPLOAD-001| Blob
  Persister -->|INT-IOTHUB-D2C-001| IoTHub
  IoTHub -. INT-ROUTE-001 missing route .-> SB
  Processor --> StorageSvc
  Processor --> FaceSvc
  Processor --> DdbSvc
  StorageSvc -->|INT-BLOB-READ-001| Blob
  FaceSvc -->|INT-FACE-*| Face
  DdbSvc -->|INT-DOCUMENTDB-001| DocDB
  Emotion -. no observed code use .-> Processor
